J, but its presence in SN 2008fp remains uncertain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2015 04:46:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Jan 2017 01:24:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-08"}
