ation\nsites at the GBj with Dy or Tb shells, leads to an increase of the coercivity\nfrom 2.5 to 3.6 T and 2.5 to 4.3 T, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2015 14:24:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Oct 2015 15:11:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-09"}
